<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287461>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Howickia trilineata group, plate 1. Howickia bicolor Marshall, sp. n.: 1, habitus. Howickia oliveri Marshall, sp. n.: 2, habitus; 3, head; 4, right wing. Howickia mercurialis Marshall, sp. n.: 5, habitus; 6, left wing. Howickia omamari Marshall, sp. n.: 7, head; 8, habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287461/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287462>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 14. Howickia trilineata group, plate 2. Howickia trilineata (Hutton): 9, habitus; 10, head. Howickia nigrilegula Marshall, sp. n.: 11, habitus; 12, head. Howickia nigriventer Marshall, sp. n.: 13, habitus; 14, head." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287462/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287463>
    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 18. Howickia myersi group. Howickia tangata Marshall, sp. n.: 15, habitus; 16, head. Howickia myersi (Richards): 17, live individual in situ; 18, habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287463/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287467>
    dc:description "FIGURES 34 – 39. Howickia mercurialis Marshall, sp. n.: 34, epandrium, posterior; 35, male left surstylus; 36, male sternite 5; 37, aedeagus and associated structures; 38, female spermathecae. Howickia omamari Marshall, sp. n.: 39, male left surstylus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287467/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287469>
    dc:description "FIGURES 49 – 52. Howickia regalis Marshall, sp. n.: 49, epandrium, posterior; 50, epandrium, left lateral; 51, male sternite 5; 52, aedeagus and associated structures." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287469/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287465>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23 – 24. Howickia exasperata Marshall, sp. n.: 23, epandrium, left lateral; 24, male sternite 5." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287465/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.287470>
    dc:description "FIGURES 53 – 56. Howickia myersi (Richards): 53, epandrium, posterior; 54, epandrium, left lateral; 55, male sternite 5; 56, aedeagus and associated structures." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/287470/files/figure.png" ;
